{
  "name": "Wind Release Dust Wind",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Wind.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You generate a strong wind from your lungs with a single breath. When you exhale you kick up a cloud of dust, dirt, and other loose debris in the target radius. Creatures who are in the affected range must make a Wisdom Saving throw. On a failed save, affected creatures cause Swirl and are considered blind until the end of their next turn on a failed save. On a successful save no further effects are applied.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the size of the cone by 10ft</p>",
